vote.title: Ordinances granting (1) a D-1 Liquor Control Overlay; (2) a Specific Use Permit for the sale of alcoholic beverages in conjunction with a general merchandise or food store greater than 3,500 square feet use; (3) a Specific Use Permit for a mini-warehouse use; and (4) a resolution accepting deed restrictions volunteered by the applicant on property zoned a CR-D Community Retail District with D Liquor Control Overlay on the southeast corner of Military Parkway and North St. Augustine Road - Z189-221(CT) - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
